# Golden render snapshots MUST stay LF-normalised on every OS. renderAss emits
# "\n"; if git rewrote these to CRLF on checkout (autocrlf), the Legacy byte-compat
# suite would fail spuriously on Windows/CI. Pin them to LF so the guard is stable
# and cross-platform. Applies regardless of the repo/user core.autocrlf setting.
golden/__snapshots__/**/*.ass text eol=lf
